4:
I've been in love with you for a long
time! H-here... This chocolate is for
you!
6: Th-thank you... I... I love you too!
9:
My job here as witness is done.
Congrats, you two.
12:
Th-thank you all so much. I couldn't
have confessed without your help!
14:
Nah, we didn't do much. It's about
time we head off though. Take care!
23:
That couple was our last request for
the morning, right?
27:
Yes. We have seven more in the
afternoon.
30:
S-sorry... It's my fault that suddenly
everyone thinks that their love will
come true if you guys cheer them
on.
35:
It's fine. At least we don't have to do
much more than watch.
40:
Feels bad to watch other people get
together when my own love life isn't
going anywhere.
45:
D-don't worry! I'll support your love,
Reticia!
48:
Um, you already gave Alk your
chocolate, right?
52:
Yeah. Remember the first time we
met? I ended up giving him the
chocolate from then.
58:
Wait, weren't we talking about giving
all your friends chocolate then?
62:
Yeah. I gave everyone else
chocolate too.
67:
What?! So you didn't prep special
chocolate, just for Alk?
73: I don't plan on giving him that.
87: So what I'm hearing is you WANT to?
93: Why are you all ganging up on me?!
98:
Because we care about you and
your love life!
102:
L-listen, I've already been rejected
once before.
105:
...Though I guess that whole thing
was a mess, and I don't plan on
giving up on my feelings...
107:
Still, I don't want to bother him when
he's got so much on his plate now.
112: Ew, you're being so proper about it.
127: She is a nice person, after all.
131:
See, Stella gets it! I'm only doing
what's right!
135:
Keep that up, and someone else'll
take the chance to run away with
him.
143:
Enough about me! What about you,
Nate? Isn't there someone you want
to give chocolate to?
146: Wait. Don't tell me. Is it Themis?
150:
Why the hell would you bring her
up?!
153:
Well, it's not like she hasn't been
trying to get your attention...
158: Me and her are NEVER happening.
177:
N-now hold on! I did give him
chocolate, but it's not what you think.
179:
I gave it to him as a friend! It was
store-bought too, since he could
cook up something way better than
me in the first place.
182:
Besides, you know me. I don't know
anything about romance or
whatever!
186:
Seriously, you're reading too much
into this!
192: I see how it is now.
203:
Both of you are a pain in the butt
because you don't realize your own
feelings!
206: What is that supposed to mean?
210:
It means that more and more
people will start to go after my man
while I'm here trying to be patient!
213:
Nate here reminded me that Alk is
too nice to everyone!
224: I'm going to give him that chocolate!
231:
...I guess the most important thing is
we convinced you to do it in the end.
234:
Excuse me... I submitted a request
for you to help me confess, but... are
you busy with something else?
237:
Oh, I'm sorry. We lost track of time,
but we're totally good to help you
out.
240:
Don't you worry about a thing. I,
Reticia Felder, will be witness to your
love.
244:
And I, too, will make sure I get my
own happy ending!
